These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
House: colonial, modern, victorian, farmhouse
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person drinking cola is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the colonial house is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| House   | colonial   | victorian | modern | farmhouse        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, pony, horse
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, musician, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the musician is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the fisherman##1
6. the person driving the roller is the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Pet        | pony   | fish | chinchilla     | horse      |
| Job         | lawyer | musician | social-worker | fisherman |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, tennis, skateboarding, sailing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, canadian, indonesian, russian
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the russian is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the russian is on the right of the indonesian##1
7. the person who's sport is basketball is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Sport         | basketball | tennis | skateboarding | sailing |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian    | russian | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, sprite, lemonade
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the freelancer is the person driving the train##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the firefighter is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking water is the freelancer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the project-manager is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Job         | architect | project-manager | freelancer | firefighter |
| Beverage       | hot-chocolate     | lemonade      | water     | sprite      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, video-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, horror, thriller, western
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, april, september, july
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
6. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3     |      4       |
| Hobby         | singing   | video-games | drawing  | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | epic        | western  | horror       |
| Birthday         | december | september    | april | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, weightlifting, parkour, skiing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the person who's sport is basketball is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person who's sport is skiing is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Sport           | weightlifting | parkour | skiing | basketball |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

