.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, superhero, comedy, zombie
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | iced-tea | mirinda | 7up        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Movie-Genre        | superhero    | comedy   | zombie  | musical |

