.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, purple, blood-red, ivory
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, metal, rock, trance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, skateboarding, skiing
1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the fan of trance##1
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Color         | ivory | purple    | black        | blood-red |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Sport         | sailing   | lacrosse | skateboarding | skiing  |

