4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the chef##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
